# SUPER IMPORTANT MINDSET

## Ye yaad rakh:

```text
Callback = "jab kaam ho jaye tab ye function chala dena"
```

---

# Ek Ultimate Example

```js
setTimeout(() => {
   console.log("Hello");
}, 2000);
```

Meaning:

```text
2 second baad callback run karo
```

---

# Final One-Line Understanding

```text
Callback is just a function that another function executes later.
```

---

# Interview Level Definition

> A callback is a function passed as an argument to another function which is executed later by that function.

---

# Sabse Important Confusion Clear

## Ye:

```js
myFunction(callback)
```

matlab:
- callback PASS hua

---

## Ye:

```js
myFunction(callback())
```

matlab:
- callback ABHI RUN ho gaya

Ye dono me huge difference hai 🔥



