## What are environment variables?

```text
Variables whose values depend on the environment in which the app runs.
```

---

## Why use them?

- secrets
- configs
- deployment differences

---

## How access them?

```js
process.env
```

---

## Data type?

```text
String
```

Always.

---

## Should .env go to GitHub?

```text
NO ❌
```

---

# Ultimate One-Line Understanding

```text
Environment variables let your app behave differently in different environments without changing the source code.
```